.. table:: Key Features
   :align: center
   :width: 100%
   :widths: auto

   +-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | .. centered:: |product|                                                                                                 |
   +=======================+=================================================================================================+
   | **CPU**               | Intel® Celeron® J6412, 2GHz, Quad-Core, 1.5M Cache, TDP=10W                                     |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **GPU**               | Intel® HD integrated GPU, 512MB shared memory                                                   |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **RAM**               | Default 4GB, maximum 32GB, 1 x DDR4 3200 SO-DIMM                                                |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Display**           | |dispsize| LCD, resolution |res| \px, brightness |bright|                                       |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Storage**           | Default mSATA 64GB SSD; 1 x SATA2.5 HDD 1T; 1 x M.2 2280 NVMe PCI-E 3.0 x 2 Slot                |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Touch**             | |tscreen|                                                                                       |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Audio**             | Realtek High Definition Audio Codec, MIC/Line-Out, Amplifier                                    |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **USB**               | 4 x USB 3.0 Type A HOST                                                                         |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **LAN**               | 2 x RJ45, 1Gbps (Realtek)                                                                       |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **UART**              | Default 4 x RS232 (2 of 4 can be configured as RS485)                                           |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **GPIO**              | 8 x General Purpose I/O (GPIO) channels, ITE 8786E Chip                                         |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **3G/4G/LTE/5G**      | |opt_1|                                                                                         |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **WiFi/BT**           | |opt_2|                                                                                         |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Expandability**     | 2 x Mini-PCIe (One for optional WiFi/BT/3G/4G/5G, one for mSATA)                                |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **HDMI**              | 1 x HDMI out                                                                                    |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Power IN**          | From 9V to 30V DC                                                                               |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Power Consumption** | |pwr|                                                                                           |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **OS**                | Ubuntu 20.04(default), Windows 7, Windows 10                                                    |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Operating Temp.**   | From -20°C to +60°C (with SSD)                                                                  |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Storage Temp.**     | From -30°C to +80°C                                                                             |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Humidity**          | From 5% to 95% relative humidity (no condensation)                                              |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Dimensions**        | |dim|                                                                                           |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **EMC**               | CE/FCC/ROHS/ISO-9001                                                                            |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Mounting**          | VESA 100mm, Panel mounting with fixtures, Wall, Desktop                                         |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Weight**            | |weight|                                                                                        |
   +-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+


